        <div class="tleft dtext">
          <!-- WT_003 -->
          <p>BallroomDJ 4 (BDJ4) is a music player designed for desktop and
laptop computers (and will work on some tablets).
It is designed to be able to play music for the
entire evening without any intervention.</p>
          <!-- WT_004 -->
          <p>BDJ4 is highly customizable and provides facilities
to organize ballroom dance music and create song lists, automatic
playlists and sequenced playlists.</p>
          <!-- WT_005 -->
          <p>BDJ4 runs on Windows, MacOS and Linux.</p>
          <!-- WT_006 -->
          <p><b><a target="_blank"
              href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/ballroomdj4/files/"
              >Download BallroomDJ 4</a></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(<span>latest version</span> <b>#VERSION#</b>)</p>
          <!-- WT_007 -->
